last_episode_to_air.name: Vengence Wore a Unitard
last_episode_to_air.overview: Carlo Gambini tracks the Falcones to Regina. He’s there to kill Cheech… or is he there just to see Gina again. Gina’s faced with a choice: side with the only boy she’s ever “like-liked” or save Uncle Cheech from certain death.

name: Fugget About It
overview: Fugget About It is a Canadian adult animated sitcom created by Nicholas Tabarrok and Willem Wennekers for Teletoon's Teletoon at Night block. The show is rated 18A for sexuality, violence, and swearing. The show was created from the Pilot Project contest on Teletoon.

episodes.name: Hate Crime Legislation is for Pussies
episodes.overview: Jimmy and Cheech take Petey to a boxing gym to "learn a few moves". After Petey enters a real fight, McCool warns Jimmy the publicity could put their witness protection in jeopardy.

episodes.name: The Full Mountie
episodes.overview: McCool takes on extra jobs to pay back a gambling debt to Jimmy.

episodes.name: Screw You, Mr. Wonderful
episodes.overview: Jimmy becomes jealous when Petey befriends a wealthy businessman. Gina convinces Theresa to pose as her mother to collect a baby bonus check.

episodes.name: The Man With No Ass
episodes.overview: Jimmy and McCool compete to prove who is the better man. Petey seeks Theresa's advice to get girls.

episodes.name: Cousin Sammy Dies in the End
episodes.overview: When the mob orders a hit on Jimmy's cousin, he arranges for him to join him in witness protection in Saskatchewan.

episodes.name: Rainbows and Painted Hos
episodes.overview: Cookie throws Jimmy out after his insensitivity crosses a line. Gina reacts with anger when her siblings won't play with her.

episodes.name: Chokin' and Tokin' in the Queen City
episodes.overview: After a near-death experience, Jimmy becomes a vigilante to make up for his past bad deeds.

episodes.name: Al Capone Wears Ladies Underwear
episodes.overview: Jimmy and Cheech take Gina to nearby Moose Jaw to search for Al Capone's hidden vault. Theresa is rejected by a blind classmate who can't see how hot she is.

episodes.name: Petey Gets God'd
episodes.overview: Petey discovers God when Jimmy sets him up with a hooker.

episodes.name: The Oracle of Vagina
episodes.overview: Jimmy helps Cookie open a fortune-telling business, then has to make all her "predictions" come true.

episodes.name: The Horny Bastard
episodes.overview: Jimmy opens Regina's first strip joint, but is shocked when his daughter starts working there as a stripper.

episodes.name: Sex on Ice
episodes.overview: Cookie starts to think Jimmy is cheating on her when he's actually pursuing a career as a masked ice-sculptor called "Jinksy".

episodes.name: Hunts With Handgun
episodes.overview: After Cheech insults a Native American, Jimmy and Cheech go to a cultural sensitivity seminar. Cookie forces Gina to join Field Girls to show up a snobby neighbor.

episodes.name: The McFrugals
episodes.overview: Jimmy gets a credit card and takes his family on a spending spree.

episodes.name: Mennonites!
episodes.overview: Theresa falls in love with a young Mennonite man and visits his community ... where she almost destroys their traditional way of life.

episodes.name: Too Cool for Night School
episodes.overview: Jimmy's job at the tourism bureau is in jeopardy because he doesn't have a high school diploma, so Jimmy enrolls in night school and starts acting like a teenager.

episodes.name: The Broadfather
episodes.overview: Jimmy goes through a crisis when he meets his long-lost father - who abandoned Jimmy years earlier to become a woman.

episodes.name: Royally Screwed
episodes.overview: A documentary about Jimmy called "Diary of a Dirty Snitch" airs on TV. The Falcones are portrayed as self-serving scumbags.

episodes.name: You Only Try Haggis Once
episodes.overview: Cookie gets a job at a Scottish restaurant leaving Jimmy to take care of the family.

episodes.name: From My Cold Limp Hands
episodes.overview: Jimmy has an identity crisis when McCool forces him to give up his guns.

episodes.name: The Fugly American
episodes.overview: A hotshot FBI agent promises to relocate Jimmy and the family back to America ... but he's really plotting to kill Jimmy and Cheech for the mob.

episodes.name: The Man from P.I.G.L.E.T.
episodes.overview: When Petey becomes a Junior Police trainee, Jimmy mentors a street kid in the ways of crime.

episodes.name: Pizza with Extra Cheech
episodes.overview: Jimmy discovers a consultant on a film shooting in Regina is passing himself off as Cheech Falcone.

episodes.name: The Balls on This Room
episodes.overview: Jimmy winds up being stalked by his Russian dance partner after he and Cookie face-off in a ballroom dancing contest.

episodes.name: Ass-Jax
episodes.overview: When Theresa creates a successful fashion accessory, her newfound wealth and independence threatens Cookie's authority.

episodes.name: Effin' Neighbors, Eh?
episodes.overview: Jimmy can't stand it when the annoying Hosers next door are given protected status by the Canadian Government.

episodes.name: Havana Kill Castro
episodes.overview: McCool takes the Falcones to Cuba on vacation. Jimmy hates it for being a ‘Communist hell-hole’, but cheers up when he discovers that killing Castro can get him ‘Super-Made' and land him back on top in New York.

episodes.name: Universal Prostitution and Pizza Fridays
episodes.overview: Jimmy calls Cheech a ‘Bum', doing the worst thing one goodfella can do to another: telling him the truth about himself. Cheech decides to run for Mayor of Regina to prove he's not a bum.

episodes.name: Just Stuck It in That There Doo-Dad
episodes.overview: When Cookie finds a photo album of Jimmy’s gumars (girlfriends) from the old life (Cheech’s fault), Jimmy takes her away for a romantic weekend and they wind up at a swinger's convention (again, Cheech’s fault).

episodes.name: Confetti Deathblow
episodes.overview: Through a misunderstanding, Cookie starts to think Petey is gay. She does her best to support him, but is shocked when it turns out he's not gay, he's into LARP (Live Action Role Playing).

episodes.name: Jimmy Gets Goosed
episodes.overview: Jimmy's boss Toby makes him take anger management then invites Jimmy over for dinner to meet his horrible mother. Cheech starts dating Greta, but Jimmy thinks he’s only trying to steal a valuable statue she owns.

episodes.name: Casino Loyale
episodes.overview: Jimmy convinces Regina Tourism to open a casino. He winds up being a big casino boss, but gets into a rivalry with Cookie when she gets hired to run the native casino. Petey gets accepted into the popular group at school.

episodes.name: Vagina's Got Talent
episodes.overview: Cookie enters Theresa in Regina's Got Talent to stick it to a rival mother who's son is a three-time winner. Theresa wants to do her own songs, but Cookie makes her do middle-of-the-road stuff to impress the judges.

episodes.name: New York State of Blind Drunk
episodes.overview: Jimmy, Cheech, and McCool get hammered one night and awaken in Jimmy's old house in New York. They have to get out of New York but keep running into the mob. Petey finds an old picture of Cookie with a man who looks like him, who he thinks is his real dad.

episodes.name: Cookie's Ovary-actin'
episodes.overview: When Cookie gets baby fever and wants another kid, Jimmy refuses to sleep with her. Problem is, he “feels the need” but can’t find a place to “empty the tanks”. Theresa, Gina, and Petey house-sit for one of McCool’s colleagues.

episodes.name: Royal Canadian Groping Pariah
episodes.overview: When Jimmy sees a seemingly compromising picture of McCool with Theresa (it’s totally innocent), he ruins McCool’s life and gets him kicked off the force. Petey’s iPhone app is stolen by Richard Wheatthin’s company.

episodes.name: What the F#@K Is the Grey Cup
episodes.overview: Jimmy and Cheech become big CFL fans and invite the Saskatchewan Rough Riders over for a barbecue. The entire team gets food poisoning on the eve of the Grey Cup. Jimmy forms a team to play the Grey Cup in their place.

episodes.name: Saskquatchewan
episodes.overview: Jimmy and Petey go on a hunting trip and come home with a Sasquatch (Dave Foley). Jimmy learns how hard McCool's job is when he has to babysit the Bigfoot. Meanwhile, Cheech winds up as a seeing eye dog for a blind woman he's attracted to.

episodes.name: Nonna You Business
episodes.overview: Jimmy’s aged great-grandmother from Italy is dying so McCool arranges for her to visit Regina. Jimmy and the family have to fool Nonna (Andrea Martin) into thinking they still in live in New York and are mafia bigshots.

episodes.name: Layin' Some Pipeline
episodes.overview: Jimmy and Cheech help the premiere of Saskatchewan pass a controversial law that brands anti-oil pipeline protestors as terrorists. Problem is, Petey was protesting the pipeline and is now a wanted man. Jimmy has to go on the lam with Petey.

episodes.name: Keepin' up With the McFelchers
episodes.overview: Jimmy’s new neighbor turns out to be a Quebec biker who’s also in witness protection. Jimmy is banned from associating with him, but then realizes his new pal is about to commit a heist. Jimmy has to stop the robbery… or join in.

episodes.name: Horse Springs Paternal
episodes.overview: Horse gets Jimmy and Cheech’s new racehorse pregnant so they sue McCool. In order to pay the boys back, McCool must track down his deadbeat dad, Staunch McCool. As McCool reconnects with his dad, Jimmy realizes the guy is a con-man who’s taking advantage.

episodes.name: Hot, Wet, Amphibious Summer
episodes.overview: Petey gets a summer job at the tourism bureau and lies about Regina history while running a bus tour. His lies prove so popular that Petey is promoted and becomes Jimmy’s boss. When Jimmy is disobedient at work, Petey fires him.

episodes.name: An Unmarried Bra Whisperer
episodes.overview: When Cookie discovers that Jimmy was engaged to someone else when he met her, but never mentioned it, she moves out. Now living on her own, Cookie finds a job as a bra-fitting consultant and proves to be a genius at the job.

episodes.name: Spicy Apocalypse
episodes.overview: In an effort to raise money to send Petey to an underwater science school, Jimmy sells a formula Cheech invented for spice neutralizer to Wheatthin. When the formula is stolen, the family must investigate the crime and find the culprit.

episodes.name: Vengence Wore a Unitard
episodes.overview: Carlo Gambini tracks the Falcones to Regina. He’s there to kill Cheech… or is he there just to see Gina again. Gina’s faced with a choice: side with the only boy she’s ever “like-liked” or save Uncle Cheech from certain death.
